{"tid":1689473,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"神獸剝藍光豬","createTime":"2019-11-02T21:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:12:04.000Z","uid":270133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c202490c2870e4c4242407658f76b9e77989f1de","tid":1689473,"uid":270133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T21:45:18.000Z","msg":"剝光豬好醜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但千祈千祈唔好整傷蛋蛋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好鬼痛㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直頭生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果男人無咗蛋蛋，就唔再係男人㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整傷咗，手尾好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有機會喪失人生樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有蛋先有男性嘅尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要好好保護蛋蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慎防猴子偷桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c96db25fc5eb3118c4f14084c4715b760087299","tid":1689473,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T21:48:12.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4c41ff759016f2677c744aa91db5f7a7fe39b0ee","tid":1689473,"uid":270133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人理"}]}